      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 295,
      "message": "ServiceBusinessLogic.createService does validations and returns Either<Service, ResponseFormat> whereas ResourceBusinessLogic.createResource() returns Resource object. \nThat's why the code added looks different in the service if block compared to resource else block.\nI have added validation for service name and system name setting. I haven't added partner service type check so that in future this API can be invoked for other service types too",
